  <CalDefinition Description="GIS-350-232 Maximal out-of-control number: (see GIS-350-1306) If the recommendation value for adaptation is set to 0 for a maximal out-of-control number I, hence adaptation has shut itself of for I times, then the recommendation value is not set back to 1 anymore and adaptation deactivates itself" Name="Maximaloutofcontrolnumber" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
