  <CalDefinition Description="GIS-350-247 Deactivation frequency adaptation: (see GIS-350-1401) Parameter to manually and externally deactivate and reactivate the adaptation process. Default value is 1 to disable adaptation process. When value is set to 0, adaptation is activated." Name="Deactivationfrequencyadaptation" References="" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
