  <CalDefinition Description="GIS-350-237 FC task data bound: (see GIS-350-1308) real number FC task data bound is the lower bound of most frequently requested task data obtained from the last updated prior probabilities Prior (O) as specified in GIS-350-90. Abnormal frequency changes are controlled for all task data above this lower bound." Name="FCtaskdatabound" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
