  <CalDefinition Description="GIS-350-244 Score redistribution range: (see GIS-350-1202) real or natural numbers in the same range as the speech systems confidence scores. They represent the upper and lower bound  [Max post  Min post ] for the range of confidence scores after redistribution of the adapted scores" Name="Scoreredistributionrange" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
    <CalID>_47ylcMY-EeOpjZKz3hOPiA</CalID>
