    </Integer>
  </CalDefinition>
  <CalDefinition Description="GIS-350-303 Domain number of tasks: (see GIS-350-2500) List of natural numbers TD for each domain, for which expertise level adaptation is done. If the number of performed tasks within a given time frame is larger than TD, prompts for this domain may be set from &#x201c;Informative&#x201d; to &#x201c;Efficient&#x201d;" Name="Domainnumberoftasks" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,VCU">
